data.description: Explore the charm of this Stuart townhouse at Trillium Townhomes. With 1400+ sqft, 3 beds, 2.5 baths, and a master suite boasting a double sink and walk-in closet, this residence offers a cozy living and dining space. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a spacious island. Wood plank tiles grace the first floor, while the upstairs features carpeting and a TV area. The property, nearly new, was briefly lived in by the owner.For those seeking a tranquil and secure community, look no further! Within walking distance to shopping and surrounded by 100+ restaurants, this townhouse provides both serenity and convenience. Enjoy Downtown Stuart and the beach, complemented by a lanai area and a one-car garage. Do Not Miss Out!
